":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三和親中既仲幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢開鋪無幾耐食過1次已經ban 三和。</blockquote><br />\n紅蜻蜓執埋有時被迫幫親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家開返啦，可以去幫襯返"},{"pid":"cdd31d7fa9c6519a0d0762add2910b7614477138","tid":212104,"uid":12001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連鎖果間瑞士咖啡室？<br />\n<br />\n呢間撚屌野連基本煮個公仔面都失敗<br />\n<br />\n垃圾</blockquote><br />\n其實呢架咩集團？<br />\n北角炮台山好多間用唔同名開但裝修一樣<br />\n又瑞士咖啡室又紅磡冰室又伯諾餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}